{"tid":1876131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】消息指瑪嘉烈兩確診者　符出院準則　一人最快今日出院","createTime":"2020-02-12T08:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T09:45:15.000Z","uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb3a2ca4af501c20256302935664fe9647ef905","tid":1876131,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"武漢新型冠狀病毒疫情持續，本港至今錄得49宗確診個案，當中1人死亡，其餘病人仍在多間醫院留醫。有醫管局消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，瑪嘉烈醫院有2位病人符合出院準則，其中1人有望在今日出院。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局總行政經理（質素及標準）劉家獻曾在2月6日表示，專家會審視每宗個案的臨床情況，包括病人康復進度，及確保病人樣本對新型冠狀病毒呈陰性，身上無帶病毒才可出院。"},{"pid":"ba12ab152d7613e3e1efbdd2412407b3b6f8fdc9","tid":1876131,"uid":18546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"有咩慘過中武肺 就係中二次武肺 相信政府！唔戴"},{"pid":"a9cb82837292fff65698535a921fe7a679f9c31a","tid":1876131,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba12ab152d7613e3e1efbdd2412407b3b6f8fdc9","tid":1876131,"uid":18546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"有咩慘過中武肺 就係中二次武肺 相信政府！唔戴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"奶完一次再奶一次<br />\n100%死梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6d4efef007d3945d3ff67cd7926ee12040b2b5","tid":1876131,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"最早入院嘅應該係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085af65bc53e5409d9b380207a3a7098af4f54f6","tid":1876131,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"出院，但冇話醫好"},{"pid":"480e9bb90c3e617930e575c1a2254c50db6fe929","tid":1876131,"uid":107681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af6d4efef007d3945d3ff67cd7926ee12040b2b5","tid":1876131,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"最早入院嘅應該係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy